 "generates a spherical topology hypergraph by UV sampling.",
 "\n"
}], "Usage",ExpressionUUID->"3b00eb9e-3163-7b45-9dd6-2237a401b47a"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The result is an initial-condition object: pass it as the second argument \
of ",
 Cell[BoxData["HGEvolve"], "InlineFormula",
  FontSize->0.9 Inherited,ExpressionUUID->
  "8ba26e45-3f02-d642-a4f0-a358d1554a97"],
